---
title: Pretzel-Crusted Chicken with Roasted Broccoli and DIY Cheese Sauce
description: Game Day Pretzel Crusted Chicken with a DIY cheesy mustard dipping sauce. No matter which team you're cheering for, it's a touchdown to celebrate! An easy side of mashed potatoes makes this meal as easy as 1,2,3!
